@startuml Sequence_AI_Chat

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Chat API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "AI Service" as AI
participant "Rate Limiter" as RateLimit

== Create New Chat ==
User -> Client: Open chat widget
User -> Client: Enter message
Client -> API: POST /api/shop/chat
API -> RateLimit: Check rate limit
RateLimit --> API: Rate limit OK
API -> DB: Create chat session
DB --> API: Chat created
API -> AI: Send message
AI -> AI: Process message
AI --> API: AI response
API -> DB: Save message and response
DB --> API: Messages saved
API -> DB: Auto-generate title
DB --> API: Title generated
API --> Client: Return chat data
Client --> User: Display response

== Continue Chat ==
User -> Client: Select existing chat
Client -> API: GET /api/shop/chat/:id
API -> DB: Get chat history
DB --> API: Chat messages
API --> Client: Return messages
Client --> User: Display chat history

User -> Client: Enter new message
Client -> API: POST /api/shop/chat/:id/message
API -> RateLimit: Check rate limit

alt Rate limit exceeded
    RateLimit --> API: Rate limit exceeded
    API --> Client: 429 Error
    Client --> User: Show rate limit message
else Rate limit OK
    RateLimit --> API: Rate limit OK
    API -> AI: Send message
    AI --> API: AI response
    API -> DB: Save messages
    DB --> API: Messages saved
    API --> Client: Return response
    Client --> User: Display response
end

@enduml

